parameters: A beautiful temari ball is placed here.
The moment it was swung, the temari ball broke.
The temari ball started to move.

Then it flew around, and before I knew it, a
tremendous impact hit my face, and I couldn't see
anything.

There are three white stones placed on the
pedestal.
I tried putting all the stones back.
There are five red stones placed on the pedestal.
I tried putting all the stones back.
There are two white stones placed on the pedestal.
I tried putting all the stones back.
There are three red stones placed on the pedestal.
I tried putting all the stones back.

Good morning, Father, with the bright sun shining
this morning.

One sun in the color of the sunset, two sparkling
suns on the water surface

single fish leaps

The moon sets, and in the night sky over the
mountain, a puppy goes bark, bark, bark
